{"tid":1676430,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有個廢佬冒住生命危險去做d咁既野！！","createTime":"2019-10-26T12:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T05:35:54.000Z","uid":325884,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0979d3e6c90e214959ec353f2210df29d4e06ef1","tid":1676430,"uid":325884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"果個就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說上星期知道左係東九區有兩位參選區議員，係擺街站宣傳既時候遇襲，感到非常震驚同憤怒，自己乃廢佬一名，希望可盡些少綿力，幫助一些年青候選人，以身體支持及保護佢地。<br />\n終於去搵左我本區既區議員，當然係有黃色認證架啦，提出左希望能夠當義工的要求，以協助佢地擺街站宣傳時出席，一來加大聲勢，又可以身體力行保護佢地，雖然我唔打得都睇得下。<br />\n今日終於收到電話，有候選議員(不同區的)接受左我請求，黎緊一個月我都會出席，直至到選舉完畢為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然我同佢傾好，要配合跟住落黎既集會時間，黎緊既集會我都一定會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n27/10 尖沙嘴見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n決一不可<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"c884c108930ccc72bb523320f0546e2ce2a574e1","tid":1676430,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eb9608021b33ab6ca2555735665dcee385fda6","tid":1676430,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打<br />\n大家可以行多一步主動幫手"},{"pid":"4368f448b47163fe1639d96a520370ac8ab8e0cf","tid":1676430,"uid":323588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:38:37.000Z","msg":"廢老好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"h